U%3D&h=034e2e60\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=kxyYVD4FjhQ&amp;feature=youtu.be</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n812行動：<br />\n一、<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">塞鐵</span></strong>（有幾組人，自己用連登搜索搵TG GRP）<br />\n二、機場<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">「警察還眼」明天1PM全民入機場 百萬人塞爆機場</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n無時間文宣<br />\n見POST者，自行Copy開新Post，要連登全部都係呢個Post<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n812起 1PM，有人性既你立刻罷工，百萬人進入機場，咩都唔做，勢要討回雙眼<br />\n機場因為100萬人係機場而暫停運作，不是們的責任，是因為機場不夠大<br />\n圍到出青馬，都全條橋唔夠闊<br />\n<br />\n統一口號，兩句，要入健力士，等歷史知道<br />\n「黑警還眼」<br />\n「五大訴求，缺一不可」<br />\n<br />\n黑警聽住：<br />\n一係你就入機場殺哂所有人<br />\n一係你就還返隻眼出黎<br />\n否則百萬人不離開機場<br />\n<br />\n不沖禁區，不沖跑道<br />\n不沖禁區，不沖跑道<br />\n不沖禁區，不沖跑道<br />\n百萬人入機場，機場自然停<br />\n百萬人入機場，機場自然停<br />\n百萬人入機場，機場自然停<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大群：<a href=\"https://t.me/airport730\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fairport730&d=bqZDxu8XrC4QaJB2SmgqvgDrJ99PsHpDQ3gYSBhgLgU%3D&h=5d0f16ee\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/airport730</a><br />\n實時Channel: <a href=\"https://t.me/hk730air\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhk730air&d=bqZDxu8XrC4QaJB2SmgqvgDrJ99PsHpDQ3gYSBhgLgU%3D&h=8634fba3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/hk730air</a>"},{"pid":"cfdd24530e00487812eef11ef7e78829d0f6ab5a","tid":1450040,"uid":290373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T17:16:32.000Z","msg":"十連自推"},{"pid":"0d907bdd5af3f3bb049d635a1d3c8823276b35dc","tid":1450040,"uid":290373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T17:16:42.000Z","msg":"十連自推"},{"pid":"9176dca8e258366ce3a3bf2055fb8043d505d93a","tid":1450040,"uid":290373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T17:16:52.000Z","msg":"十連自推"},{"pid":"6d707a765f167086632ca71598d302d8573fdc5d","tid":1450040,"uid":290373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T